msgid "Admin Single Sign-On (SSO)"
msgstr "Singolo accesso (SSO) per l'amministratore"

msgid ""
"Allow staff to sign in to the admin panel using an enterprise identity "
"provider (Microsoft Entra ID, Google Workspace, Okta, etc.) via OpenID "
